   "## Common pitfalls\n",
   "\n",
   "- Writing skills for trivial one-shot tasks (noise in catalog).\n",
   "- Loading full skill bodies into every prompt (token blowup) \u2014 use metadata + `load_skill` tool.\n",
   "- Forgetting `tool_call_count` only increments on actual dispatches.\n"
  ]
 },
